<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='753500' id='t-753500'>sitting in my office.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='756245' id='t-756245'>I really hope that others, all of you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='759234' id='t-759234'>visiting objects in the museum,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='760809' id='t-760809'>and taking them home and 
finding them for yourselves,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='763263' id='t-763263'>will allow those objects to flourish 
in your imaginative lives.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='767577' id='t-767577'>Thank you very much.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='769130' id='t-769130'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
